{"data":[{"id":563870464,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8fe8b64a44ecb547dcc414bf1dec8035","url_token":"xian-zhi-ren-xi","name":"仙之人兮","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b320b27445b271a54d79f40bddfbc698_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b320b27445b271a54d79f40bddfbc698_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8fe8b64a44ecb547dcc414bf1dec8035","user_type":"people","headline":"非典型医学生","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":123,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563870464","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a39cf916c5e400579fa612f662bd1279_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546305549,"updated_time":1546305549,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e楼上高赞几位大佬已经说得很专业了，但作为见证了 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 从几十粉涨到几万粉这一奇妙过程的数学爱好者，还是忍不住想写点啥。主要错误在两个方面，一是思路没意义，二是证明逻辑混乱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明者的总思路是把哥德巴赫猜想扩大，然后证明这个扩大的猜想，再把扩大的部分剔除出去。不看证明者的证明这个逻辑本身其实没有问题，但他的操作实在槽点满满。对于6k+2这类偶数，他想证明的是这类偶数可以写成两个素数或者一个素数与-1的和，问题就在于因为6k+3是合数，这类偶数写不成一个素数与-1的和。逻辑关系应该是不能这么扩展，但证明者的逻辑是我把他扩展开然后分类讨论的时候舍弃。这样的展开再排除的思路没有任何意义。打个比方，好比几百年来数学家们都犯愁怎么把大象塞进冰箱里，他说这个简单，我们把大象和一个小蛋糕一起放进冰箱里，再把小蛋糕拿出来就行了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e逻辑证明过程中，还是以6k+2类举例，其他同理。他想要证明的是“如果-1是素数，那么任何正偶数属于集合A”。且不论条件与结论是否有因果关系，也不论条件和结果是真命题假命题，只看他是如何论证这一变式：他打算论证逆否命题“如果存在正偶数不属于集合A，则-1不为素数”。这是证不出来的，因为“-1是素数”是他之前分类讨论时的设定，在同一讨论中不可更改替换。再看他对于此逆否命题的证明，我认为他连“存在”都没明白是什么意思，如下图：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c66f31224c4b603f36d06d402cea7034_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"856\" data-rawheight=\"198\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0a23838e0dd8ed6d433bd6792108fb87_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"856\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c66f31224c4b603f36d06d402cea7034_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='856'%20height='198'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"856\" data-rawheight=\"198\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0a23838e0dd8ed6d433bd6792108fb87_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"856\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c66f31224c4b603f36d06d402cea7034_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c66f31224c4b603f36d06d402cea7034_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e“存在”的意思应该是“客观存在一个不属于集合A的正偶数”而不是随便找一个正偶数强行让它不属于集合A。因为他“-1属于素数”的设定导致2属于集合A，而这一步的论证过程他又强行假设让属于集合A的2不属于集合A来推导-1不是素数，如此循环形成永动，数学物理两开花，岂不美哉？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，数论是数学女王的皇冠，哥德巴赫猜想是皇冠上的宝珠。我也不知道当时为什么知乎给我推送 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 的宣言，当时只觉得就算是营销号就算是钓鱼问题也要关注，看看到底是哗众取宠还是单纯的不知天高地厚。现在看到了证明也只是希望他能脚踏实地不要投机取巧，没有基础不要好高骛远，更不要随便轻视几百年来无数为哥德巴赫猜想倾注心血的数学家们。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"楼上高赞几位大佬已经说得很专业了，但作为见证了 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 从几十粉涨到几万粉这一奇妙过程的数学爱好者，还是忍不住想写点啥。主要错误在两个方面，一是思路没意义，二是证明逻辑混乱。证明者的总思路是把哥德巴赫猜想扩大，然后证明这个扩大的猜想，再把扩…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=152\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled